{"_id":"2iult41Jehz0F1O8","name":"Broken Leg (Major)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A bone is badly broken, either resting at an odd angle or has splintered at the point of breakage. The Hit Location is effectively unusable until healing.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Leg: </span>Reduce your Move by half permanently and suffer a &ndash;20 penalty to all Tests that rely on mobility, and you cannot use the Dodge skill at all.</p>\n<h3>Healing</h3>\n<p>A fracture takes 40+1d10 days to heal. At the end, a successful <strong>Average (+20) Endurance</strong> test means the bone healed well. Otherwise: Permanent loss of -10 to Agility</p>\n<p>A successful <strong>Average (+20)</strong> Heal Test within a week of receiving the fracture will negate the need for Endurance Test. But the area must remain bound and held in place for the duration of healing. If binding is undone, another <strong>Average (+20) Heal</strong> Test enacted within a day will need to be passed to avoid the Endurance Test.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Leg","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-20 to mobility Tests, cannot use Dodge, half Move","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"30 + 1d10","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/broken-leg.png","effects":[{"_id":"ZwCU28eoOKqibVfu","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prePrepareData","effectApplication":"actor","script":"args.actor.data.data.details.move.value /= 2","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/broken-leg.png","label":"Movement Penalty","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"tZayAMRUW6AVaa12","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Relies on mobility","modifier":-20,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null},"preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/broken-leg.png","label":"Broken Leg","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"3S4OYOZLauXctmev","name":"Torn Leg Muscle (Major)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A muscle has been sprained or torn, impairing your capabilities. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Leg:</strong> Half movement, Suffer a penalty of -10 to all Tests involving the leg</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Healing: </span>The muscle will partially heal in 30 &ndash; your Toughness Bonus days, after which the penalty for using the limb reduces to &ndash;10 to all relevant Tests. The muscle will completely heal after another 30 &ndash; your Toughness Bonus days. Use of the Healing skill does little but inform you not to use the affected Hit Location.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Leg","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"30 - TB","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornleg.png","effects":[{"_id":"e5BPTZkHGMJuDX2p","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Tests involving leg with Torn Muscle","modifier":-10,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null},"preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornleg.png","label":"Torn Leg Muscle","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"t1Anp3f9yR4IJqpR","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prePrepareData","effectApplication":"actor","script":"args.actor.data.data.details.move.value /= 2","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"start