{"_id":"7rBhIRo96Mydo0Cv","name":"Torn Body Muscle (Minor)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A muscle has been sprained or torn, impairing your capabilities. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Body:</strong> Suffer a penalty of -20 to all Tests involving the body</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Healing: </span>The muscle will partially heal in 30 - Toughness Bonus days. Use of the Healing Skill will reduce the time by 1 day, plus a further day per SL (can only gain this once)&nbsp;</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Head","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"30 - TB","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornhead.png","effects":[{"_id":"Aans92KGaO90qXGV","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Involves the body","modifier":-10,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null},"preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornhead.png","label":"Torn Body Muscle","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"8piWcBKFlQ2J1E3A","name":"Amputated Ear","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Ear</strong>: Losing an ear is painful, but you will soon learn to live without it. Should you have the bad luck to lose both your ears, permanently suffer a penalty of &ndash;20 to all hearing-based Perception Tests. Further, you suffer a penalty of &ndash;5 to all Fellowship Tests per ear lost when others can see your earless state</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Ear","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedear.png","effects":[{"_id":"i6SjnYZ0pNeN8SNZ","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prefillDialog","effectApplication":"actor","script":"if (args.type == \"characteristic\" && args.item == \"fel\")\n      args.prefillModifiers.modifier -= 5\n\n    else if (args.type == \"skill\") {\n      if (args.item.data.characteristic.value == \"fel\")\n        args.prefillModifiers.modifier -= 5\n    }"}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedear.png","label":"Lost Ear","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"NjLgGWim2CMWdOL4","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Hearing based Perception test","modifier":-20,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null}}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedear.png","label":"Lost Both Ears","tint":"","transfer":false}]}
{"_id":"EaqlLRQigwnsEAXX","name":"Broken Body (Major)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A bone is badly broken, either resting at an odd angle or has splintered at the point of breakage. The Hit Location is effectively unusable until healing.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Body: </span>Strength and mobility is severely limited: -30 to Strength and Agility Characteristic, half your Move.&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Healing</h3>\n<p>A fracture takes 40+1d10 days to heal. At the end, a successful <strong>Average (+20) Endurance</strong> test means the bone healed well. Otherwise: Permanent loss of -10 to Agility</p>\n<p>A successful <strong>Average (+20)</strong> Heal Test within a week of receiving the fracture will negate the need for Endurance Test. But the area must remain bound and held in place for the duration of healing. If binding is undone, another <strong>Average (+20) Heal</strong> Test enacted within a day will need to be passed to avoid the Endurance Test.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Body","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-30 to S and Ag, half your Move.","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/broken-body.png","effects":[{"_id":"l5W27AsBX8jj1T80","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prePrepareData","effectApplication":"actor","script":"args.actor.data.data.details.move.value /= 2","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/broken-body.png","label":"Movement Halved","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"qIkF1AGNf4XxzaFv",