{"_id":"SYjWiKDzMS6CtROJ","name":"Amputated Finger","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Finger</strong>: Further, you suffer a penalty of &ndash;5 to all Tests using the hand in question per finger lost. Once 4 or more fingers are lost on a hand, use the rules for a severed hand.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Finger","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-5 using <specific hand>","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedfinger.png","effects":[{"_id":"DaOXNCrHEMsOleGx","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectApplication":"actor","preventDuplicateEffects":false,"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectData":{"description":"Lost Fingers","modifier":-5,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null}}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedfinger.png","label":"Lost Fingers","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"SpPRZZRHxly7uo2G","name":"Amputated Nose","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Nose:&nbsp;</strong> A loss of a nose leaves one looking freakish in the extreme. Suffer a permanent loss of &ndash;20 to your Fellowship and suffer a penalty of &ndash;30 to all Tests involving the sense of smell.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Nose","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-20 Fellowship, -30 to smell Tests","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatednose.png","effects":[{"_id":"OTeQYlJcacd8ID4i","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectApplication":"actor","preventDuplicateEffects":false,"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectData":{"description":"Involving Smell","modifier":-30,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null}}},"changes":[{"key":"data.characteristics.fel.modifier","value":-20,"mode":2}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatednose.png","label":"Amputated Nose","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"UytN3fDREi3JuKST","name":"Torn Head Muscle (Minor)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A muscle has been sprained or torn, impairing your capabilities. &nbsp;</p>\n    <p><strong>Head:</strong> Suffer a penalty of -10 to all Tests involving the head</p>\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Healing: </span>The muscle will partially heal in 30 - Toughness Bonus days. Use of the Healing Skill will reduce the time by 1 day, plus a further day per SL (can only gain this once)&nbsp;</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Head","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"30 - TB","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornhead.png","effects":[{"_id":"y2XL7QrWlGI6aloz","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Involves the head","modifier":-10,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null}}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornhead.png","label":"Torn Head Muscle","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"ZhMADOqoo0y8Q9bx","name":"Amputated Toe","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Toes: </strong>Loss of toes has an adverse effect on your balance. For each toe lost, suffer a permanent loss of &ndash;1 to your Agility and Weapon Skill Characteristics.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Toes","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/injury.png","effects":[{"_id":"n47pJamskjv7bbXl","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectApplication":"actor","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[{"key":"data.characteristics.ws.modifier","value":-1,"mode":2},{"key":"data.characteristics.ag.modifier","value":-1,"mode":2}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/injury.png","label":"Amputated Toe","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"eWPN3CV2Eddwz8aM","name":"Torn Body Muscle (Major)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A muscle has been sprained or torn, impairing your capabilities. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Body:</strong> Suffer a penalty of -20 to all Tests involving the body</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Healing: </span>The muscle will partially heal in 30 &ndash; your Toughness Bonus days, after which the penalty for using the limb reduces to &ndash;10 to all relevant Tests. The muscle will completely heal after another 30 &ndash; your Toughness Bonus days. Use of the Healing skill does little but inform you not to use the affected Hit Location.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Body","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-20 to Tests involving the Body","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"30 - TB","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornbody.png","effects":[{"_id":"VczyyG2FDfvOQflT","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Involves the body","modifier":-20,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null},"preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornbody.png","label":"Torn Body Muscle","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"fBcZhOBn8IpoVqQ1","name":"Amputated Teeth","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Teeth:&nbsp;</strong> Loss of teeth may be unsightly and can make eating difficult. For every two teeth you lose you also suffer a permanent loss of 1 from your Fellowship characteristic. Further, once more than half your teeth (Humans: 16; Elves: 18; Halﬂings and Dwarfs: 20) are lost, you find consuming solids significantly more difficult than your peers, doubling eating times, and making some foodstuffs nigh-on impossible to eat, which is largely a matter of roleplaying and narrative description of your actions.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Teeth","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/injury.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"gz2xy41OSVZ8YBgI","name":"Amputated Foot","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Foot</strong>: Reduce your Move by half permanently and suffer a &ndash;20 penalty to all Tests that rely on mobility, such as Dodge. Losing both feet makes it hard to walk. Perhaps you could hire a henchman to carry you?</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Foot","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-20 to mobility Tests, half Move","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedfoot.png","effects":[{"_id":"vFwI36wK9QnfgLGG","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prePrepareData","effectApplication":"actor","script":"args.actor.data.data.details.move.value /= 2","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedfoot.png","label":"Movement Halved","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"QHpPBISp2DCIRZp7","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Relies on mobility","modifier":-20,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null},"preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedfoot.png","label":"Amputated Foot","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"hCadFsTRvLN9faaY","name":"Broken Head (Major)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A bone is badly broken, either resting at an odd angle or has splintered at the point of breakage. The Hit Location is effectively unusable until healing.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Head:</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span>Down to a liquid diet and will suffer a penalty of -30 to all Language Tests.&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Healing</h3>\n<p>A broken bone takes 40+1d10 days to heal. At the end, a successful <strong>Challenging (+0) Endurance</strong> test means the bone healed well. Otherwise: Penalty of -10 to spoken Language Tests.</p>\n<p>A successful <strong>Average (+20)</strong> Heal Test within a week of receiving the fracture will negate the need for Endurance Test. But the area must remain bound and held in place for the duration of healing. If binding is undone, another <strong>Average (+20) Heal</strong> Test enacted within a day will need to be passed to avoid the Endurance Test.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Head","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"40 + 1d10","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/head.png","effects":[{"_id":"WLwNpLVQX79yOsdJ","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prefillDialog","effectApplication":"actor","script":"if (args.type == \"cast\" || (args.type == \"skill\" && args.item.name.includes(game.i18n.localize(\"Language\"))))\n   args.prefillModifiers.modifier -= 30","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/head.png","label":"Broken Head","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"k00PimCWkff11IA0","name":"Amputated Leg","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Whenever you suffer a Critical Wound marked Amputation (Difficulty) you must pass an Endurance test of the corresponding difficulty or gain a @Condition[Prone] Condition. On a Failure (-2) or worse, you gain a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; on an impressive Failure (-4 or worse), gain an @Condition[Unconscious] condition</p>\n<p>All amputations require Surgery to heal properly, meaning 1 Wound cannot be healed until you visit a surgeon. See @JournalEntry[Healing]{Surgey}</p>\n<p><strong>Leg:&nbsp;</strong> Reduce your Move by half permanently and suffer a &ndash;20 penalty to all Tests that rely on mobility, but cannot use the Dodge Skill. Losing both feet makes it hard to walk. Perhaps you could hire a henchman to carry you?</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Leg","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-20 to mobility Tests, cannot use Dodge, half Move","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":true},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedleg.png","effects":[{"_id":"p9uFm2XY1RGrjStF","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prePrepareData","effectApplication":"actor","script":"args.actor.data.data.details.move.value /= 2","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedleg.png","label":"Movement Halved","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"wkJy3QCy8odqGvjm","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectApplication":"actor","preventDuplicateEffects":false,"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectData":{"description":"Relies on mobility","modifier":-20,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null}}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/amputatedleg.png","label":"Amputated Leg","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"nF5z1OEhpi4t6a6S","name":"Torn Leg Muscle (Minor)","permission":{"default":0,"oTi5e7Dr05zb56mO":3},"type":"injury","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A muscle has been sprained or torn, impairing your capabilities. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Leg:</strong> Half movement, Suffer a penalty of -10 to all Tests involving the leg</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Healing: </span>The muscle will partially heal in 30 - Toughness Bonus days. Use of the Healing Skill will reduce the time by 1 day, plus a further day per SL (can only gain this once)&nbsp;</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"location":{"value":"Leg","type":"String","label":"Location"},"penalty":{"value":"-10 to Tests involving (specific) Leg","type":"String","label":"Penalty"},"duration":{"label":"Duration","value":"","type":"String","active":false,"permanent":false},"source":{"type":"String","label":"Source"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornleg.png","effects":[{"_id":"73XsH9pZ8Qymz0kN","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"prePrepareData","effectApplication":"actor","script":"args.actor.data.data.details.move.value /= 2","preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornleg.png","label":"Movement Halved","tint":"","transfer":true},{"_id":"ErAJc8kPnAwubY1m","flags":{"wfrp4e":{"effectTrigger":"dialogChoice","effectApplication":"actor","effectData":{"description":"Involves leg with Torn Muscle","modifier":-10,"slBonus":null,"successBonus":null,"difficultyStep":null},"preventDuplicateEffects":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"modules/wfrp4e-core/icons/injuries/tornleg.png","label":"Torn Leg Muscle","tint":"","transfer":tr